      • getSenseNumber

        public String getSenseNumber(String senseKey)
        Consumes a sense key of a lexeme and returns it's sense number
        Parameters:
        senseKey - the sense key of a lexeme, for which sense number should be returned
        Returns:
        sense number of the lexeme associated to the consumed senseKey or null,
        if index.sense file parsed by this instance of IndexSenseReader contains no entry for the consumed senseKey
